Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:03.55,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,100)}{\pos(320,320)}誓约胜利之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:11.08,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,10)}{\pos(320,320)}魔女的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让他白白死去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然失去了Archer 就要在此打倒Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.77,Niaoyu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「 Neun, Acht, Sieben 」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:24.26,Niaoyu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「 Stil, schießt Beschießen ErschieSsung 」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}九号      八号      七号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}全财投入          敌人                片甲不留
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker 把她捏碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker 快点干掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混账
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她放开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 快点离开 Master
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她放开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别使用这招 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外…别无选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是解开结界就这副样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你无法使用这把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在现实中敌不过的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去幻想能赢得了的武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来制造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到的 也仅限于此了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所使用的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把剑是 我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本不应该破碎的剑之所以会破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我的想象有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投影 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该挑战的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能有一丝的差错与妥协
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想定基本构造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复制构成材质
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重现累积年月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌驾 完成诸多工程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于此 幻想凝聚成剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 明明不可能赢过Berserker的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经制造出超越Berserker的剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却没办法使用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的剑吗 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 Caliburn  选定国王的石中剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\fnsimhei}Caliburn：{\fn方正隶变简体}必胜黄金之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我永远失去了的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟只是那个男人制造出来的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能再次存在的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 这份幻想也不可小看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然仅以普通的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就毁灭了我的身体七次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要对伊莉雅下手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然Berserker已经不存在了 那伊莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 Saber 大清早就一脸忧郁的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是做了一场梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子我放这了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要喝点牛奶 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么头好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什么 大清早就这么豪华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 和式汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太散漫了 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然Berserker已经不存在了 当然会散漫点的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的Servent
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对现在的Saber来说只不过是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于战斗 并没有十拿九稳之说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦虚了 谦虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与亚瑟王对决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些泛泛之辈的英雄来多少也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经察觉到Saber是谁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜意识地察觉到了 但到了昨天我确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能使用那把圣剑的英雄 这世上惟有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 你今后到底打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在客室里睡着的那个危险的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确的说 不是在客室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在士郎的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我… 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 我也要说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然收留伊莉雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能丢下她不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且伊莉雅还只是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让你吃尽了苦头 你还说这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉雅只要有人好好管教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会再做那样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我之所以战斗不是为了杀死Master
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了终结战争而战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 伊莉雅斯菲尔所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全都原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不原谅她对Archer做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 Servant到最后反正都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在意这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不配做Master了 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你致谢 Saber之Master
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对身为敌人的我的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我表示衷心的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客套话不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊 这是我的份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让开 你这无礼者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 在吃饭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好没礼貌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 收容伊莉雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对有百害而无一利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不会有危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉雅已经不是Master了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还是Master
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失去Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要令咒还在就还是Master 不是告诉过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对Servant而言也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失去Master
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在消失前仍然有或多或少的延缓期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一那样的流浪Servant和这家伙缔结契约…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会和其他Servant在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉雅的Servant 永远都只是Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果士郎输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber就由我来收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无意成为你的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你这样也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不管是我赢 还是Saber保护士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并非这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 你也对士郎说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没注意听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再说一次 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了 我反对在这里窝藏伊莉雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂 你刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允许你这么胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉雅 快吃早餐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎的选择 说不定是无上的妙策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是锻炼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber该说是没尽全力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是故意手下留情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正似乎没动真格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说起来 的确比以往消极了点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不从正面来得更猛烈些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我没帮助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从…从正面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的话亦有可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定身体会碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然在对打 那当然无可避免了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃 士郎的料理做得真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么 Saber不是讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并没有敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且士郎又把你当作客人招待了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也要尽最低程度的礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 对不起 我没想到你会在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能否先让出浴室一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎要清洗身体是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会对Master的行动限制到那种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不像凛那样富有少女的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望被士郎过多地看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样充满肌肉的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在男士眼里一定很难看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就这样 再…再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿都没坏啊 真难以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了那么厉害的投影魔术还能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投影？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 将实际存在的美术品或名剑等物质
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过自己的魔力以想像的方式再现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人类的想像不是千疮百孔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那是无法复制得和真货一模一样的半吊子魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很快就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且投影对魔力的消耗很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber之剑所含的魔力 要远超过士郎的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要进行仿造 简直是自杀行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你知道Excalibur是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起Excalibur不就是亚瑟王的代名词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有砍不断的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且不会伤损的名剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我就猜你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 真正重要的并不是剑 而是剑鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑鞘？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 只要带着剑鞘 亚瑟王就不会流血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么亚瑟王又会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了 传说中Excalibur的剑鞘是被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么啊 怎么去在意那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 我只是在想 要是那样的话就无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是我偶尔也会出错的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偶尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然远坂叫我不要使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投影 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不着 在进行头脑的操练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一天也不停地做着这样的练习？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽量这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是父亲给我规定的每日必修课
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 早上你说做了一场梦是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servant并不会做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所见到的 是你的梦 你的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master和Servant之间在精神上也是连结在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果结合变得紧密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时便会窥视到对方的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不怪Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 那个梦是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大的一场火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎和我很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能了解你的错误所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这样下去 不知道会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也一样所以能够了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能做错误的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为像父亲那样正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 这就是错误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前 凛也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎的自我献身简直不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概从一开始就没有考虑过自己的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要得到圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 士郎也一样需要圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被你召唤出来是必然的 Master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争也到了高潮阶段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只要Berserker消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就再没有什么好怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余下的敌人只有Lancer和Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力的储藏也即将达到临界值了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只需有一名充当托盘的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能把圣杯强制召来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要魔术师吗 看来我无法派上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为祭品的魔术师只要使用其他的Master便可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况是作为圣杯的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要富有卓越的潜在能力的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从能力上讲最理想的莫过于这位大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她稍微野了点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要的只是魔术师的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能成为卓越的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么能否使用魔术就无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你会派上点用场呢 小姐
